            "title": "屯門黃金海灣•意嵐錄二手獲利  250萬元成交 持貨2年升值25%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15872227&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中原地產碧堤半島分行表示，新近促成屯門黃金海灣第一期意嵐5B座低層J室二手買賣成交，實用面積215平方呎，開放式間隔，向東南，最近收樓後速以250萬元沽出，實用呎價11628元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原業主於2024年3月以200.1萬元一手買入單位，持貨約兩年，帳面獲利49.9萬元，單位升值25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">黃金海灣最近陸續收樓入伙，放盤量逐漸增加，其中開放式戶目前約有20個放盤，最平叫價240萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15872227-%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e9%bb%83%e9%87%91%e6%b5%b7%e7%81%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 09:08:11",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "新世界柏傲莊III單日售出逾50伙 套現逾12.8億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=15870225&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新世界發展(00017)與港鐵(00066)合作的港鐵大圍站上蓋「柏傲莊III THE PAVILIA FARM III 」單日沽出52伙大宅，套現逾12.8億。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"柏傲莊III 售樓情況\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"柏傲莊III 售樓情況\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">柏傲莊III 售樓情況</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">售出單位包括8伙四房雙套、15伙四房一套、29伙三房單位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">成交價及呎價最高一伙為第8座(8A)48樓A單位，屬四房雙套連工作間及洗手間設計，實用面積1210平方呎，成交價4356萬，呎價3.6萬。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「柏傲莊III」是次採取「雙線銷售」策略，除了臨河三、四房單位採用招標形式發售，內園單位亦以價單形式發售。周四上載第1A號價單，集團稱｜現正與合作伙伴商討，研究短期內加推單位應市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">項目已取得滿意紙，現樓可以即買即住。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870225-%e6%96%b0%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e6%9f%8f%e5%82%b2%e8%8e%8aiii%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e5%94%ae%e5%87%ba%e9%80%be50%e4%bc%99-%e5%a5%97%e7%8f%be%e9%80%be12-8%e5%84%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/20260414_PP_PAVILIA-FARM_00017_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-15 09:08:11",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
